markdown: 26 <::chart: Line graph showing percentage production of New Hampshire pullets during trial 7. The y-axis is labeled "Percentage production" and ranges from 50 to 100. The x-axis is labeled "Weeks on experiment" and ranges from 0 to 24. The graph includes a legend indicating four different experimental groups based on % Molasses and % Napier: - Solid line: % Molasses 0.0, % Napier 3.0 - Dashed line: % Molasses 8.0, % Napier 4.0 - Solid line with 'x' markers: % Molasses 16.0, % Napier 5.0 - Dotted line: % Molasses 24.0, % Napier 6.0 The x-axis also indicates "Pretest" from week 0 to 2 and "Interim" from week 2 to 4. Fig. 1. Percentage production of New Hampshire pullets during trial 7.::> Source: https://www.industrydocuments.ucsf.edu/docs/tlyl0226
